{
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {
          "type": "grafana",
          "uid": "-- Grafana --"
        },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### KMS / etcd Encryption \u2014 User Journey SLIs\n\nMonitors the health of customer-managed etcd encryption (KMS) across all HCPs.\n\n**SLO Targets:** Availability 99.95% | Errors <0.05% | Latency p99 <500ms | DEK Cache >0 | Status Check <5min",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.999
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0.9995
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "avg(hostedClusterAPI_valid_azure_kms_config{status=\"True\"})",
          "legendFormat": "KMS Availability"
        }
      ],
      "title": "KMS Availability (ValidAzureKMSConfig)",
      "description": "SLO: 99.95% over 30 days.\n\nGood: 100% (green) \u2014 all HCPs have valid KMS config, Key Vault is reachable.\nBad: <99.95% (red) \u2014 one or more HCPs cannot access their KMS key. Check Key Vault network access, key status, and managed identity permissions.",
      "type": "gauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.0003
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.0005
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "(sum(kas:kms_operations_errors:rate5m{namespace=~\"$hcp\"}) or vector(0)) / sum(kas:kms_operations_total:rate5m{namespace=~\"$hcp\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Error Rate"
        }
      ],
      "title": "KMS Error Rate",
      "description": "SLO: <0.05% error rate over 30 days.\n\nGood: 0% (green) \u2014 all KMS encrypt/decrypt operations succeed.\nBad: >0.05% (red) \u2014 KMS operations are failing. Common causes: Key Vault throttling, key revoked, private endpoint unreachable.\n0% with no data means no operations are happening (idle cluster).",
      "type": "gauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.3
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.5
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (apiserver_envelope_encryption_kms_operations_latency_seconds_bucket{namespace=~\"$hcp\", method_name=\"/v2.keymanagementservice/encrypt\", grpc_status_code=\"0\"}))",
          "legendFormat": "Encrypt p99"
        }
      ],
      "title": "KMS Encrypt Latency (p99)",
      "description": "SLO: p99 <500ms.\n\nGood: <100ms (green) \u2014 encrypt operations complete quickly.\nWarning: 300-500ms (yellow) \u2014 latency increasing, may indicate Key Vault throttling or network issues.\nBad: >500ms (red) \u2014 encrypt latency exceeds SLO. Impacts secret creation and certificate rotation speed.",
      "type": "gauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "min(kas:kms_dek_cache_size:min{namespace=~\"$hcp\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Min Cache Size"
        }
      ],
      "title": "DEK Cache Size (min)",
      "description": "SLO: >0 at all times.\n\nGood: >0 (green) \u2014 DEK cache has keys, most operations served from cache.\nBad: 0 (red) \u2014 cache empty, every secret read/write makes a round-trip to Azure Key Vault. This is a performance cliff and reliability risk.",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "barWidthFactor": 0.6,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {
              "type": "linear"
            },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true,
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "none"
            },
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "off"
            }
          },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "SLO Target (99.95%)"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "red",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.lineStyle",
                "value": {
                  "fill": "dash",
                  "dash": [
                    10,
                    10
                  ]
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.fillOpacity",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 10
      },
      "id": 6,
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "hostedClusterAPI_valid_azure_kms_config{status=\"True\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{ name }}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(0.9995)",
          "legendFormat": "SLO Target (99.95%)"
        }
      ],
      "title": "KMS Availability per Cluster",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "pluginVersion": "11.6.9",
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "hideZeros": false,
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "description": "Per-cluster KMS availability over time. The green line shows ValidAzureKMSConfig=True (1=valid, 0=invalid). The red dashed line is the 99.95% SLO target.\n\nGood: Line at 100%, overlapping with or above the SLO target.\nBad: Line drops below the SLO target \u2014 the cluster's KMS key became inaccessible."
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "barWidthFactor": 0.6,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {
              "type": "linear"
            },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true,
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "none"
            },
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "off"
            }
          },
          "unit": "ops",
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 10
      },
      "id": 7,
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (namespace, grpc_status_code) (rate(apiserver_envelope_encryption_kms_operations_latency_seconds_count{namespace=~\"$hcp\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ namespace }} ({{ grpc_status_code }})"
        }
      ],
      "title": "KMS Operations Rate by Status",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "pluginVersion": "11.6.9",
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "hideZeros": false,
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "description": "KMS gRPC operations per second, broken down by numeric gRPC status code.\n\nGood: Only code '0' (OK) visible \u2014 all operations succeeding.\nBad: Non-zero codes appearing (1=CANCELED, 4=DEADLINE_EXCEEDED, 14=UNAVAILABLE) \u2014 indicates KMS provider connectivity issues.\nNormal rate: ~0.03-0.15 ops/s (mostly status checks every 30s)."
    },
