        "tooltip": {
          "hideZeros": false,
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "description": "Cumulative p99 latency for KMS encrypt and decrypt operations. The red dashed line is the 500ms SLO target.\n\nGood: Lines well below the 500ms target (typical: 30-100ms).\nBad: Lines approaching or exceeding the 500ms target \u2014 Key Vault may be throttling or network is degraded."
    },
