          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "description": "DEK (Data Encryption Key) cache size on each KAS pod. The cache stores recently used encryption keys to avoid round-tripping to Key Vault.\n\nGood: All pods show consistent cache sizes >0.\nBad: Any pod drops to 0 \u2014 that pod will hit Key Vault for every operation. Inconsistent sizes may indicate pod restarts."
    },
